Package: XAgent
Type: Package
Title: Modular AI Agent Framework for News, Data, and Interaction
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Oliver", 
           email = "olee7149@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    XAgent is a modular R framework for building intelligent agents that can read RSS feeds, 
    analyze financial and macroeconomic data, and interact with users through Telegram, local chat files, or email. 
    It includes components for state management, emotional modeling, LLM prompt composition, and data API integration.
